parameters:
Even the doctor doesn't know... Haru-kun... what
on earth happened to you...?

No... The one who's suffering the most is Haru-
kun... I don't have time to break down...!
There must be something I can do...!

(Lately, it seems like I haven't been eating
much...)

Alright, now that it's decided, let's prepare
dinner at the shopping district.
